graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller<br/>Go Operator]
        HealthCheck[Health/Readiness<br/>8081/TCP]
        Metrics[Prometheus Metrics<br/>8080/TCP]

        Controller -->|exposes| HealthCheck
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
    end

    subgraph "DSP Stack Components (per DSPA)"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>8443/8888/8887]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent]
        ScheduledWF[Scheduled Workflow Controller]
        WorkflowController[Workflow Controller<br/>Argo v3.4.17]
        MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>StatefulSet]
        Minio[Minio<br/>S3-compatible]
        UI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>Optional]
        MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>OAuth2]
        MLMDgRPC[MLMD gRPC Server<br/>9090/8080]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        DSPA[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
        Workflow[Workflow CR<br/>Argo]
        CronWorkflow[CronWorkflow CR<br/>Argo]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPA
    DSPA -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|reconciles| APIServer
    Controller -->|reconciles| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|reconciles| ScheduledWF
    Controller -->|reconciles| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|reconciles| MariaDB
    Controller -->|reconciles| Minio
    Controller -->|reconciles| UI
    Controller -->|reconciles| MLMDEnvoy
    Controller -->|reconciles| MLMDgRPC

    APIServer -->|creates| Workflow
    ScheduledWF -->|creates| CronWorkflow
    WorkflowController -->|executes| Workflow

    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    PersistenceAgent -->|syncs status| MariaDB
    MLMDgRPC -->|stores lineage| MariaDB

    APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    Workflow -->|stores outputs| Minio

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio]
        S3[External S3]
        ExternalDB[External MySQL]
    end

    Controller -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    WorkflowController -->|creates pods| K8sAPI
    APIServer -->|authenticates| OAuth
    MLMDEnvoy -->|authenticates| OAuth
    Controller -->|exports metrics| Prometheus
    APIServer -.->|mTLS optional| ServiceMesh
    APIServer -.->|production| S3
    APIServer -.->|production| ExternalDB

    subgraph "ODH/RHOAI Integration"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        DSC[DataScienceCluster]
    end

    Dashboard -->|manages| DSPA
    Dashboard -->|embeds UI| APIServer
    DSC -->|installs| Controller

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style DSPA fill:#f5a623
    style APIServer fill:#4a90e2
    style WorkflowController fill:#4a90e2
    style MariaDB fill:#7ed321
    style Minio fill:#7ed321
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8
    style OAuth fill:#e8e8e8
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321
    style DSC fill:#7ed321
